        "TileImage": "$($repository aec4fafc-c21e-4261-877e-2402210ec798).Image",
        "Description": "Mr Yuan was fired from the ICA several months ago and has since lost his home as well.\r\rOur personality analysis indicates with 97% probability that he will seek revenge by leaking confidential data from the Agency, and it appears Ms Tyrrell has been protecting him - we&apos;ve discovered evidence of her attempting to hide these results.\r\rIn the event that you are seen or recorded in the facility, we want to be able to pin the crime on Mr Yuan so be sure to dress as him.\r\r[Escape via Block Manhole]",
